{
  "stem": "14002.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Finally a couple days later-- still, they didn't give us any food or water in that-- in that-- for that boat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Finally, after a couple days, we came to a city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think it was Linz, in Austria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They took us out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went out from the boat, five in a line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we started to march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Who-- whoever couldn't march, whoever-- whoever got sick or couldn't-- or couldn't march or got slow, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] they shot him, right there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The rest of us had to march again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so till-- till we came to Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] In Ebensee, itself, I didn't work, because it was already-- they realized already, the Germans realized already that the war is-- is close to an end.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In Ebensee, we didn't get-- we didn't receive almost nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The people there, they were dying on the-- on the street, in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was-- it was something, you know, undescribable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they just took them, as the person-- as the person died, they just took him on a wagon and out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think-- I think in the whole time I was in Ebensee, they fed us once.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And what that feeding was, I-- it was a soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I mean it was hot water with potato peels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You were lucky if you got the potato peels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I think that was once or twice the most in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Till finally, May 7, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Americans came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But before the Americans came in, there was two days where there was actually nobody there, no authority there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was only the German civilians outside, no SS or anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was free-for-all in Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
